channel.title: Just opened my own repost account called green shell
channel.description: Hello producers! I just made my own repost account on SoundCloud called green shell. On green shell I will repost chill tracks that I like. Please go and give it a follow and submit your tracks! https://soundcloud.com/green-shell-528049881

item.title: Just opened my own repost account called green shell
item.dc:creator: Peregrihn
item.description:
I’m not trying to be rude but what’s the point of a repost account that has little to no followers? I’m just looking at this from a logical standpoint… If you can get followers who will listen then good on you but until then, I don’t know… thanks for the follow though. I guess you could start following people and hope they follow back, like I did, and then they mention you to others and the cycle continues. Just throwing a little feedback at you on this decision
